{"tid":1564860,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你即係想你好? 為你好先屌你?","createTime":"2019-09-13T02:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T02:45:11.000Z","uid":249170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0508f4614f1dcbaccf2cd575a13a75772a77a1ca","tid":1564860,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:33:53.000Z","msg":"仲有幾多人信<br />\n同事屌你即係想你好? 緊張你先屌你，教精你袋錢入你袋? 唔緊張你屌你都費事?<br />\n唔好打飛機啦<br />\n<br />\n上司係為佢自己好先屌你<br />\n可以顯得自己有威嚴，踩低你枱高自己<br />\n比老闆知你唔掂，自己勁過你<br />\n同埋屌完人發洩完個人會爽左，工作效率會提升，反而比人罵果個工作效率會廢左<br />\n<br />\n同你職位相同或者低級過你既屌你仲撚慘，證明你無料到比人食住"},{"pid":"7a189464ef5343f62b5c4f887932c0d411efeb90","tid":1564860,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:34:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"c51757780f17db66c897ff7626d59c33f050f1b5","tid":1564860,"uid":180117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:45:11.000Z","msg":"好多人都鐘意屌人<br />\n但冇人會鐘意比人屌"}]}